 1. Install Python (preferably a recent one, but 2.4+ should work)

 2. Install napkin with
    make install

 3. Get the easy-rsa suite from OpenVPN and configure it

 4. Generate a master certificate with
    ./pkitool --server <server hostname>

 5. Put the master certificate in /etc/napkin/master.{crt,key}

 6. Generate agent certificates for all clients with
    ./pkitool <hostname>

 7. Put agent's certificates in /etc/napkin/agent.{crt,key}

 8. Start napkin-master using the initscript or the command

 9. Create manifests for your hosts in /var/lib/napkin/master/manifests/<hostname>

10. Set the master in /etc/sysconfig/napkind like
    NAPKIND_ARGS="--master napkin.example.com"

11. Start napkind using the initscript
